{"tid":2143804,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"11.11「三罷」女生攜索帶准守行為 三男涉攜鐵鎚煮食油不認罪候審","createTime":"2020-08-07T09:53:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-07T11:22:11.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cd91ad934615f1fe6e5eaccc6fc6d9828518e8d9","tid":2143804,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T09:53:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200807/5BZVFU2VUPHD4H252Y7G5J7APM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200807%2F5BZVFU2VUPHD4H252Y7G5J7APM%2F&d=ACvVw7CXGjn4pyDVYlJlLGWzMblEAwKPRhfqpO9yGDY%3D&h=fa1672f8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200807%2F5BZVFU2VUPHD4H252Y7G5J7APM%2F&h=1150e5c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200807/5BZVFU2VUPHD4H252Y7G5J7APM/</a><br />\n<br />\n有網民於去年11月11日發起「三罷」，堵塞各區交通。四名年輕男女被指凌晨在天水圍天瑞邨一帶管有索帶、打火機和鐵鎚等物品，被控管有物品意圖損壞財產等罪。案件今午在屯門裁判法院再訊，被控管有一包索帶的16歲女學生獲准以1,000元簽保守行為一年結案，控罪撤銷。餘下被指管有鐵鎚、打火機等的三人，則否認控罪，准保釋至下月8日作審前覆核。"},{"pid":"c5863a0aafee111ea556fc99352d5073e21bc40f","tid":2143804,"uid":220985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T10:17:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"135e85923a050def227c1974c37db253778ba445","tid":2143804,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5863a0aafee111ea556fc99352d5073e21bc40f","tid":2143804,"uid":220985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T10:17:35.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T10:19:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itd